                            </a>
                            <h3>
                                <a href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/miss-regular-customer-wants-to-enjoy"
                                    title="Miss Regular Customer Wants to Enjoy">Miss Regular Customer Wants to Enjoy</a>
                            </h3>

                            
                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 56"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/miss-regular-customer-wants-to-enjoy/chapter-56">
                                Chapter 56
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">69,609</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>Izumi, a university student part-timing at a manga cafe, got curious about a regular customer. Her name is Honami, a high school girl who&#039;s been coming to the manga cafe recently. This defenseless and seemingly cute girl who he can&#039;t take his eyes off of has a secret...!?This is a slightly naughty, heartful love comedy where this gentle pair will get to &quot;enjoy&quot; their youth to the fullest!! </p>
                              <div class="read-more-wrap">
                                <a class="read-more" href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/miss-regular-customer-wants-to-enjoy" title>Read more</a>
                              </div>
                                                    </div>

                        
                        
                                                                    
                        <div class="list-comic-item-wrap">
                            <a data-id="918" class="list-story-item bookmark_check cover"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/lord-of-money" title="Lord Of Money">
                                <img alt="Lord Of Money"
                                     class="lazy"
                                     src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/lord-of-money.webp"
                                     data-src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/lord-of-money.webp"
                                     width="120" height="170"
                                     loading="lazy"
                                     >
                            </a>
                            <h3>
                                <a href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/lord-of-money"
                                    title="Lord Of Money">Lord Of Money</a>
                            </h3>

                            
                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 290"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/lord-of-money/chapter-290">
                                Chapter 290
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">839,567</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>Every day was hell for Sung Changwook as he worked for the abusive Chun Joongmyung, the third son of the powerful Jikyung Group. When Changwook finally quits, Joongmyung attempts to kill him, but his plan backfires when both of them get electrocuted and switch bodies. Now stuck living as Joongmyung, Changwook must solve the mystery of his new identity and wage war against Joongmyung&#039;s older brothers for control of the company. The odds are stacked against him, but could lightning strike twice? </p>
                              <div class="read-more-wrap">
                                <a class="read-more" href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/lord-of-money" title>Read more</a>
                              </div>
                                                    </div>

                        
                        
                                                                    
                        <div class="list-comic-item-wrap">
                            <a data-id="57193" class="list-story-item bookmark_check cover"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/i-will-raise-this-family-up" title="I Will Raise This Family Up">
                                <img alt="I Will Raise This Family Up"
