                            <h3>
                                <a href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/i-will-raise-this-family-up"
                                    title="I Will Raise This Family Up">I Will Raise This Family Up</a>
                            </h3>

                            
                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 78"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/i-will-raise-this-family-up/chapter-78">
                                Chapter 78
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">385,006</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>Read I Will Raise This Family Up183cm tall. 75kg. Bench pressing 500.My body was perfect. My life was perfect.So why the he** am I stuck in this tiny, short, three-heads-tall body?!I was Jeon Seong-guk, the king of Samjeon Group, a global powerhouse!But just when I was about to claim everything, a sudden heart attack struck me down.And now?I&#039;ve been reborn as a baby in a poor family.A one-room apartment for a house?!Young, struggling parents instead of the wealthy elite?!Is this some kind of cruel joke?!But no matterbecause I am Jeon Seong-guk.I clawed my way to the top once, and I&#039;ll do it again.This time, I&#039;m not just climbing to successI&#039;m taking my entire family with me! </p>
