                            <div><span class="aye_icon">840</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>I am Lynseal the Elf. The greatest gourmet in all the elven realm! In the castle town of Fahrenheit, a man appeared, pulling a mysterious cart and serving strange dishes night after night. The dish&#039;s name is &quot;Ramen.&quot; With just one bite, the flavor is enough to send you to the heavens! In the blink of an eye, I became a prisoner to &quot;Ramen,&quot; and every night, I waited longingly for that man.

However, the man—someone I had grown close enough to call a &quot;friend&quot;—disappeared from before me after a certain night. Twenty years have passed since then, and I still stand on that same street corner, desperate for another taste of &quot;Ramen.&quot; Ah... my beloved &quot;Ramen,&quot; will I truly never encounter that flavor ever again...? </p>
